a lot of humility,

00:25:11.880 --> 00:25:15.510
because there's so much we don't
know not living in that world,

00:25:15.510 --> 00:25:18.130
but there's still
much value we can add,

00:25:18.130 --> 00:25:20.790
because we bring
a skill set that

00:25:20.790 --> 00:25:23.430
doesn't exist, for the
most part, in the sector.

00:25:23.430 --> 00:25:26.839
And so there's huge,
huge opportunity there.

00:25:26.839 --> 00:25:27.880
JACQUELLINE FULLER: Yeah.

00:25:27.880 --> 00:25:31.746
Little infomercial for
