And I apologize; I was
trying to figure out

00:32:58.550 --> 00:33:00.500
how to formulate this well.

00:33:00.500 --> 00:33:02.480
I think there's a
culture in Silicon Valley

00:33:02.480 --> 00:33:04.355
of, scale is good, right?

00:33:04.355 --> 00:33:05.980
Like, scale is the
thing that you want.

00:33:05.980 --> 00:33:06.896
And I think-- I agree.

00:33:06.896 --> 00:33:08.261
It'd be good to see more scale.

00:33:08.261 --> 00:33:09.760
I think a corollary
of this, though,

00:33:09.760 --> 00:33:12.301
is that organizations that are
trying to scale, then, kind of

00:33:12.301 --> 00:33:14.320
ignore the problems
that don't scale well.

