00:46:17.510 --> 00:46:20.270
In your research, did
you see any good example

00:46:20.270 --> 00:46:23.180
of a government
working with companies

00:46:23.180 --> 00:46:26.015
to scale their impact?

00:46:26.015 --> 00:46:28.140
ANN MEI CHANG: Government
working with-- you mean--

00:46:28.140 --> 00:46:29.639
AUDIENCE: Yeah,
like, for example, I

00:46:29.639 --> 00:46:31.970
know in San Francisco,
maybe the local government

00:46:31.970 --> 00:46:39.530
will work with companies in the
area to provide jobs for people

00:46:39.530 --> 00:46:41.600
or have an impact that
