00:46:41.600 --> 00:46:42.874
have budget for.

00:46:42.874 --> 00:46:44.040
ANN MEI CHANG: I see, I see.

00:46:44.040 --> 00:46:45.290
Yeah.

00:46:45.290 --> 00:46:49.560
So it is true that government
